</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p>Google's ecommerce documentation suggests 24 to 48 items as a reasonable range. Balance SEO efficiency against page load speed and <a href="/blog/improve-core-web-vitals/">Core Web Vitals</a> performance.</p>
