<td>Good</td>
<td>Best</td>
<td>Better</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Implementation complexity</td>
<td>Low</td>
<td>High</td>
<td>Medium</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Deep content discovery</td>
<td>Yes</td>
<td>No (without fallback)</td>
<td>No (without fallback)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
